text: Digrammia curvata, the shaded granite, is a species of geometrid moth in the family Geometridae. It is found in Central America and North America. The MONA number for Digrammia curvata is 910784 & Hodges number for Digrammia curvata is 6370. ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * * * * Category:Macariini Category:Moths described in 1880
title: Digrammia curvata
